Control file for musicsim. First two lines will be skipped by loadCtrlFile method.
PARAMETER        VALUE     	     	   COMMENT
AnodeGeom	 ../../agfiles/AnodeGeometry	   location of anode geometry file
ELossBins	 555			   Number of bins for y axis
MaxELoss	 10			   Max y value [MeV]
strip		 6			   Strip where reaction takes place. Use -1 for unreacted beam
Eres		 0.05			   Energy noise level (sigma) in each strip [MeV]
beam		 37Cl			   Use "AEl" notation, e.g. 17F where A=17 El(ement) = F
Kb		 79.0			   Beam energy as it enters the dead gas layer [MeV]
KbFWHM		 0.80			   Beam energy FWHM [MeV]
target		 4He			   
compound	 41K			   
NumEvapPart	 1			   Number of evaporated particles. E.g. 1 for 17F(4He,1H)
evap0Name	 n			   
evap0Color	 4			   Integer. See ROOT colors.
res0Name	 40K
res0Color	 3			   Integer. See ROOT colors.
SRIMbeam	 ../../LISE/files/37Cl_in_HeGas_220Torr_293K.lise
SRIMres0	 ../../LISE/files/40K_in_HeGas_220Torr_293K.lise
dEdxScaleBeam	 1.0			   Beam stopping power scale factor
dEdxScaleRes0	 1.0			   Heavy particle stopping power scale factor	
NEvents		 100			   Number of events simulated
Wait		 1			   Wait between simulated events? 1=yes, 0=no
Update		 1			   Update graphics between simulated events? 1=yes, 0=no
MaxTime		 2000			   Maximum time for an event [ns]
SimStep		 0.001			   Simulation step size [cm]
Method		 0
FileName	 traces_an_stp6_220Torr_lise_79MeV.root
FileOpt		 recreate
PrintOpt	 0

